                 "readmeSummary":  "## Instagram Comments \u0026 Replies Scraper (No Cookie)\n\nA scraper for harvesting Instagram post comments and comment replies without requiring cookies or session IDs; designed for large-scale collection of publicly visible comment data. The Actor extracts comment text, author information, timestamps, engagement metrics, content type and identifiers, and associates items with the source post; it supports optional crawling of reply threads, sorting by recent or popular comments, and high-throughput operation via rate limiting and concurrent requests to enable scalable comment harvesting and metadata extraction in JSON format for downstream analysis.\n\n## Use cases\n\n- Collect large-scale Instagram post comments (bulk scraping up to tens of thousands of comments per post).\n- Extract replies to comments to reconstruct conversation threads and comment hierarchies.\n- Obtain comment datasets sorted by recency or popularity for relevance-based analysis.\n- Support analytics workflows for developers, marketers, and analysts who need reliable comment metadata for social listening, engagement analysis, or research.",
